org.firstinspires.ftc.robotcore.internal.system

Class BmpFileWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.firstinspires.ftc.robotcore.internal.system.BmpFileWriter

  • public class BmpFileWriter
extends java.lang.Object
    A utility for saving a Bitmap as a Windows ".bmp" file. Currently, only Bitmap.Config#ARGB_8888 is supported; this could be enhanced with some small additional work.
